bio:
Hi, this is Jenny Chen from China. 

I am a qualified and experienced International Professional Chinese teacher for 9 years with more than 10000 online lessons taught on and outside of Italki. With giving 5 stars feedback to my lessons, my students have achieved their goals in the manner of:

(a)  reaching HSK 4 or HSK 5 level from “ZERO”;
(b)  speaking Chinese fluently like a native speaker;
(c)  obtaining high scores in IBDP Chinese and AP Chinese;
(d)  succeeding in the developing of Chinese
